BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION
*SOLUTION*

Let's multiply this out so that we can easily use the power rule:

>> [`` r(x)=4x^4+4x^5+x^6``] <<

Then,

>> [`` r'(x)=4(4x^3)+4(5x^4)+6x^5=\boxed{16x^3+20x^4+6x^5}``] <<


END_PGML_SOLUTION

